macro.name: DAQ_AI_PORT_NAME
macro.description: Port name for AI DAQ Port. Defaults to cDAQ9185-MUONFEMod3

macro.name: DAQ_AO_PORT_NAME
macro.description: Port name for AO DAQ Port. Defaults to cDAQ9185-MUONFEMod4

macro.name: CURR_FREQ
macro.description: Sample rate in Hz for reading separator current. Defaults to 1000

macro.name: CURR_NELM
macro.description: Number of samples read from separator current. Defaults to 1000

macro.name: VOLT_FREQ
macro.description: Sample rate in Hz for reading separator voltage. Defaults to 1000

macro.name: VOLT_NELM
macro.description: Number of samples read from separator voltage. Defaults to 1000
